text: We had a reunion dinner here for 13pax. They can accommodate large group at special request.  The chef originally comes from Zhejiang Province and has pretty good culinary skill in Hunan cuisine.  It is at a quiet corner of Orchard Towers, which has been recently revamped with many new eateries:)
Marvellous dices and value for money meals...fel so good like my mum home cook meals! Love it so much! Friendly services...nice quiet corner on the four floor of Orchard Tower!
Nice home cook food. Cosy place and very reasonable price.

Food is fabulous and price reasonable. Wl go back to patronise.

JoAngie
Delicious Chinese cuisine, and reasonable price
